ref_desc = "[b][color=light_blue]Section:[/color] 4.5[/b]
The Near Infrared Imager and Slitless Spectrograph like other instruments covers a wide variety of functions like imaging and spectrography. The specialized function only the NIRISS has is aperture mask interferometry. "
